    <listitem>
      <para>
        Explain the benefits of model driven development with reference to tecnology neutral design 
        and architecture. List 5 benefits of using URDAD for the technology neutral design.
        (15 points)
      </para>
    </listitem>
      
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Explain the difference between a failure and a fault. Give an example of a fault and
        discuss strategies you could use to prevent this fault leading to a failure. (5 points)
      </para>
    </listitem>
      
    <listitem><para>
      Consider a typical online travel agent.
      <orderedlist>
        <listitem><para>
          Discuss the high level architectural requirements for the travel agent with reference to
          scope of services, quality requirements and integration requirements.
          (20 points)
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          Discuss the architectural patterns you would like to choose for the core systems 
          infrastructure and how they would be combined.
          (20 points)
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          Discuss the strategies you would like to employ to realize realiability, scalability and integrability.
          (20 points)
        </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          Discuss the possible use of reference architectures.
          (20 points)
        </para></listitem>
      </orderedlist>
    </para></listitem>  
